## 5. ADR — Architecture Decision Record  *(reusable — run per decision)*

> Replace the bracket with the decision.

```
Write an ADR for: [DECISION, e.g. "Kafka for order events"].
Format (max 1 line per field except Consequences):
- Title
- Status (Proposed/Accepted)
- Context
- Decision
- Consequences (2-3 bullets: + and -)
- Alternatives considered (1 line each)

