## Token-saving cheat sheet

- Paste the manifest, not the codebase. ~200 tokens replaces thousands.
- Keep `... only. No prose.` on every prompt — biggest single saving.
- Batch related questions into one prompt ("for each service, list its top risk").
- Iterate in deltas; never regenerate a whole document to fix one line.
- Run sequence diagrams one flow per prompt — more accurate, easier to correct.
- Cache diagram *source* (Mermaid text) in the repo; regenerate visuals locally.
